<p>今天我要给大家讲故事，讲什么呢？ 故事的开始呀， 是从前有座山，山里有座庙，庙里有个老和尚，和一个小和尚，有一天，老和尚对着小和尚说，今天我给你讲个故事， 这个故事呀，就是， 从前有座山，山里有座庙，庙里有个老和尚，和一个小和尚，有一天，老和尚对着小和尚说，今天我给你讲个故事， 这个故事呀就是… and yes, we can continue for ages and this story will never end, it is good for bed time, isn't it? Because your kids will fall asleep straight away after they get bored. <br/>
I used to ask my grandmum, what’s next what’s next, later on I found out myself, well, there is no next. But those two monks are so famous in China and I believe that everyone knows about them. This is what we are going to talk today; the stories that every Chinese knows. <p/>
