<p>Because this is such a special podcast about traveling we decided to broadcast it from Phuket, Thailand. Just so that you know that we are enjoying our time in the sun, while most likely you are stuck in some office listening to our podcast.While we teach you chinese we can just float around in the blue sea.... isn't that nice?<br/>OK we are just kidding, we are not really in Phuket. We are in Xi'an. But the weather is really hot here, just like in Phuket. Although there's no sea or a river anywhere nearby we have a swimming pool just next door and if we want, we can visit the Terracotta Army. Ok... in truth we feel as miserable as all of you and we want to go on holiday. And we have been a ton of times in the Terracotta Army.
<p/>Please listen to this podcast about traveling. and leave us a comment if you are listening to our podcast somewhere nice. Make us all feel jealous ;-)<p/>
