    <item>
      <title>Advanced - Chinese Podcast - 70's 80's 90's</title>
      <link>http://www.visualmandarin.com/lessons/advanced/chinese-podcast/70's-80's-90's</link>
      <enclosure url="http://content.visualmandarin.com/resources/mp3/advanced/chinese-podcast/70's-80's-90's.mp3" length="23123" type="audio/mpeg" />
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2009 04:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
      <guid>http://www.visualmandarin.com/lessons/advanced/chinese-podcast/70's-80's-90's</guid>
      <itunes:author>VisualMandarin.com</itunes:author>
      <itunes:explicit>no</itunes:explicit>
      <itunes:keywords />
      <itunes:subtitle>This podcast talks about how people value things for those were born in the 70's, 80's and 90's.  During this period China went through many changes. People who were born in the 70's, like to work and enjoy work, they work for money, for house, for car...</itunes:subtitle>
      <dc:date>2009-06-26T04:05:55Z</dc:date>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://content.visualmandarin.com/resources/images/small_4007818872.jpg"/></p>
<p>This podcast talks about how people value things for those were born in the 70's, 80's and 90's.  During this period China went through many changes. People who were born in the 70's, like to work and enjoy work, they work for money, for house, for cars. And people who were born in the 80's, they work for their own interest, they work because they like their job, they refuse to work overtime, because that is their private time - an influence from the West. People who were born in the 90's, they refuse to work, they live on their parents, and enjoy the moment. <p/>

70's: we have bank savings<br/>
80's: we have credit cards<br/>
90's: we have rich parents<br/>
<p/>
因为社会发展的速度过快，导致三代人的强烈反差。70后已经慢慢成熟，变得世俗变得稳重；80后还在为自己最后那一点青春疯狂，不愿把舞台交付他人；90后以先声夺人之势席卷而来，只为抓住大众关注焦点；经过社会的磨练，明天的80后将是今天的70后，而90后现在的疯狂，80后也曾经历。。。因为那是一段青春的记忆。<br/>
70后：工作狂基本上都是70后的。<br/>
80后：而我们，拒绝加班！<br/>
90后 ：拒绝上班！<br/></p>]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
