      <title>Beginner - Chinese Podcast - Survival Chinese - A Marriage Proposal</title>
      <link>http://www.visualmandarin.com/lessons/beginner/chinese-podcast/survival-chinese/a-marriage-proposal</link>
      <enclosure url="http://content.visualmandarin.com/resources/mp3/beginner/chinese-podcast/survival-chinese/a-marriage-proposal.mp3" length="23123" type="audio/mpeg" />
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2009 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <guid>http://www.visualmandarin.com/lessons/beginner/chinese-podcast/survival-chinese/a-marriage-proposal</guid>
      <itunes:author>VisualMandarin.com</itunes:author>
      <itunes:explicit>no</itunes:explicit>
      <itunes:keywords />
      <itunes:subtitle>The suit cost him almost one thousand dollars and the tie was worth more than three hundred .He just came back from the hairdresser’s, feeling really excited. He was going to invite his girlfriend to an exquisite dinner and propose to her as well. He n...</itunes:subtitle>
      <dc:date>2009-05-15T23:00:00Z</dc:date>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://content.visualmandarin.com/resources/images/small_747057021.jpg"/></p>
<p>The suit cost him almost one thousand dollars and the tie was worth more than three hundred .He just came back from the hairdresser’s, feeling really excited. He was going to invite his girlfriend to an exquisite dinner and propose to her as well. He needed to look good and neat. The appointed time finally arrived. He waited impatiently in fron of the restaurant entrance. It was almost half past six and his girlfriend was nowhere to be seen. He was so anxious that he decided to ring her to make sure she was alright. The phone kept on ringing for 5 seconds before she answered. “你在做什么?” He almost shouted .” 我不能来了”. She replied, sounding quite uncaring. <p>
His heart was frozen. He never felt such coldness casting every pore in his body. Disappointment, frustration reigned. He felt the world was turning upside down and he felt like everything around was meaningless. With trembling voice, he asked at the phone, “你什么时候可以来?” she took a pause and said quietly, “我会让你知道的”.
